<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 09:14:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国国有券商将扩大在东南亚的投资银行业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-state-owned-brokerage-ramp-up-investment-banking-business-southeast-asia-2024-07-16/</link><description>国有券商中国银河证券 (CGS) 的一名高级管理人员表示，计划明年将其在东南亚的投资银行团队从目前的 30 人扩大到 50 人，并押注在市场低迷的情况下该地区的交易量会增加在家里。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:09:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-state-owned-brokerage-ramp-up-investment-banking-business-southeast-asia-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行成立新的以气候为重点的基础设施融资部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/hsbc-launches-new-climate-focused-infrastructure-finance-unit-2024-07-16/</link><description>一位高级银行高管告诉路透社，英国汇丰银行已成立一个新部门，以挖掘与世界向低碳经济转型相关的基础设施融资和项目融资交易，并聘请了一位前英国政治家来领导该部门。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/hsbc-launches-new-climate-focused-infrastructure-finance-unit-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>鉴于“致命四方”的威胁，英国将增强武装力量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-boost-armed-forces-given-threat-deadly-quartet-2024-07-16/</link><description>英国表示，将加强其“空心化”的武装部队，以确保该国做好准备面对由中国、伊朗、朝鲜和俄罗斯组成的防务审查负责人所说的“致命四方”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 07:49:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-boost-armed-forces-given-threat-deadly-quartet-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚 ADE 预计新飞机短缺导致飞机维修激增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/malaysias-ade-sees-boom-aircraft-repairs-amid-new-plane-shortages-2024-07-16/</link><description>马来西亚航空服务公司亚洲数字工程 (ADE) 首席执行官马赫什·库马尔 (Mahesh Kumar) 表示，由于新飞机短缺，航空公司将延长飞机的飞行时间，全球飞机维修行业将在未来六年出现更大增长。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 07:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/malaysias-ade-sees-boom-aircraft-repairs-amid-new-plane-shortages-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>美银表示，投资者持乐观态度，但对地缘政治持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/investors-stay-bullish-july-fuelled-by-fed-rate-outlook-2024-07-16/</link><description>美国银行周二的全球基金经理调查显示，对美国利率将下降、防止经济硬着陆的预期使投资者保持看涨情绪，尽管地缘政治构成了这种情况的最大风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 06:53:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/investors-stay-bullish-july-fuelled-by-fed-rate-outlook-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>对于全球投资者来说，中国是一个缓慢燃烧的贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-investors-china-is-slow-burning-trade-2024-07-16/</link><description>对于在中国股市持有资金的全球投资者来说，最新的经济数据并没有带来任何安慰，只是提醒他们，他们所押注的复苏需要一段时间才能实现。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 06:31:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-investors-china-is-slow-burning-trade-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国需求疲软损害了奢侈品公司历峰集团的销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-says-quarterly-sales-up-1-constant-exchange-rates-2024-07-16/</link><description>卡地亚母公司历峰集团周二表示，截至 6 月份的三个月内，该奢侈品集团的销售额几乎持平，中国需求下滑导致整体业绩略低于预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:47:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-says-quarterly-sales-up-1-constant-exchange-rates-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>ASML订单有望受益AI芯片热潮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmls-order-book-expected-benefit-ai-chip-boom-2024-07-16/</link><description>计算机芯片制造商的顶级设备供应商阿斯麦预计将在其新老板周三公布第二季度业绩时报告新订单大量涌入，因为客户扩大产能以满足人工智能芯片不断增长的需求。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:06:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmls-order-book-expected-benefit-ai-chip-boom-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国平安通过可转换债券交易筹集 35 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-ping-an-raises-35-bln-convertible-bond-deal-2024-07-16/</link><description>中国平安保险周二表示，已通过发行可转换债券筹集了 35 亿美元资金。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:03:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-ping-an-raises-35-bln-convertible-bond-deal-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国力图一箭多击 房地产救援行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-tries-hit-more-birds-with-one-stone-property-rescue-push-2024-07-16/</link><description>在北京命令中国城市购买新竣工的公寓并将其转变为经济适用房后，他们采取的第一步是公布扩大补贴资格的计划，并解决这一过程中的其他经济问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 04:07:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-tries-hit-more-birds-with-one-stone-property-rescue-push-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>暴风雨继续袭击中国，小镇遭遇全年降雨量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-shuts-train-lines-rain-arrives-chinas-north-2024-07-16/</link><description>随着今年夏天袭击南方的极端风暴转移到中部和北部省份，中国河南的一个小镇一天遭遇了近一年的降雨量。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:49:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-shuts-train-lines-rain-arrives-chinas-north-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国拖累，亚洲（日本除外）下跌，日元再次下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-16/</link><description>日本以外的亚洲股市周二小幅走低，因投资者思考特朗普获胜对中国意味着什么，而日元则恢复下滑，促使官员在上周疑似干预后发出新的警告。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:24:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>9月降息成为焦点，美元企稳，日元波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-drifts-powell-comments-bring-september-rate-cut-focus-2024-07-16/</link><description>周二，美元小幅脱离五周低点，因投资者在美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔发表评论后权衡9月份降息的理由，并考虑美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普连任的可能性上升。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 01:47:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-drifts-powell-comments-bring-september-rate-cut-focus-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国持续的需求担忧导致油价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-tick-down-worries-about-chinese-demand-2024-07-16/</link><description>由于担心中国经济放缓抑制需求，油价周二下跌，尽管人们越来越一致认为美联储最早可能在 9 月份开始降息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 00:27:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-tick-down-worries-about-chinese-demand-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>Hugo Boss因中国和英国需求疲软而下调全年预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hugo-boss-cuts-full-year-sales-guidance-over-weaker-demand-china-uk-2024-07-15/</link><description>德国时装公司 Hugo Boss 下调了今年的销售和盈利预期，理由是全球消费者需求疲软，尤其是中国和英国，导致其股价下跌多达 10%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 22:30:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hugo-boss-cuts-full-year-sales-guidance-over-weaker-demand-china-uk-2024-07-15/</guid></item></channel></rss>